OL,3,CKing's Speech: Killers to be forced
OL,4,Cinto sentencing hearings under
OL,5,COlivia's Law
OL,7,FMany people in the UK - until a
OL,8,Fstring of high profile cases - had
OL,9,Fbeen unaware that killers and rapists
OL,10,Fare legally allowed to skip their
OL,11,Fsentencing hearings.
OL,13,FBut that is set to change, thanks in
OL,14,Fpart to the mother of nine-year-old
OL,15,Fmurder victim Olivia Pratt-Korbel,
OL,16,Fwho has successfully campaigned for
OL,17,F"Olivia's Law", after her daughter's
OL,18,Fkiller Thomas Cashman stayed in his
OL,19,Fprison cell instead of attending
OL,20,Fcourt.
